   281	The redundancy with the standalone `implementer-host` service is
   282	intentional: both can claim implement tasks, the user picks which
   283	they prefer. The chunk-9c implementer module is for human
   284	override / debugging; `implementer-host` is the unattended scripted
   285	worker. They race for the same tasks via `Store.claim` (which has
